Dialogue: 0.0:00:12.62.0:00:13.87.Default..0.0.0..Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:13.87.0:00:15.95.Default..0.0.0..Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:15.95.0:00:19.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Unidentified male.\Nappears to be in his mid-thirties.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:18.29.0:00:19.58.Default..0.0.0..What a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:19.54.0:00:23.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}hit by a truck. unconscious\Nand in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:19.58.0:00:23.70.Default..0.0.0..He's done for.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:23.70.0:00:25.91.Default..0.0.0..The driver of the truck is unhurt.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:25.91.0:00:29.04.Default..0.0.0..Oh. yeah. I was hit by a...
Dialogue: 0.0:00:32.83.0:00:35.66.Default..0.0.0..Two high school students\Nthought to have also been hit
Dialogue: 0.0:00:35.66.0:00:37.20.Default..0.0.0..are currently missing.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:37.20.0:00:38.58.Default..0.0.0..A search is underway.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:38.58.0:00:41.04.Default..0.0.0..Requesting immediate backup. Over.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:41.04.0:00:44.91.Default..0.0.0..Did those three make it out okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:44.91.0:00:48.20.Default..0.0.0..He's heavy! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:48.20.0:00:49.66.Default..0.0.0..You bet I am.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:49.66.0:00:54.66.Default..0.0.0..I've been a recluse for 20 years.\NI just had to bang on the floor for food.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:54.66.0:00:57.74.Default..0.0.0..Zenith! Anipa bayhebu! La took!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:57.74.0:00:59.24.Default..0.0.0..Hm?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:03.33.0:01:05.33.Default..0.0.0..Do you know where you are?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:05.33.0:01:08.49.Default..0.0.0..Pipe down. You don't have to shout.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:08.49.0:01:11.79.Default..0.0.0..Epabuhia! Akunaja taku! La took!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:11.79.0:01:13.41.Default..0.0.0..Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:13.41.0:01:14.29.Default..0.0.0..Blood pressure dropping!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:14.29.0:01:15.58.Default..0.0.0..Prepare a transfusion!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:15.58.0:01:16.83.Default..0.0.0..Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:16.83.0:01:18.58.Default..0.0.0..Do you know your name?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:18.58.0:01:19.79.Default..0.0.0..Can you speak?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:19.79.0:01:22.87.Default..0.0.0..Huh? Am I dying?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:22.87.0:01:26.58.Default..0.0.0..Oh. well. my life was basically over anyway.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:27.99.0:01:31.58.Default..0.0.0..I wish I could've at least lost my virginity.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:32.58.0:01:36.20.Default..0.0.0..Epabuhia! Tauwka seio kwa! Pahail za!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:36.20.0:01:39.49.Default..0.0.0..Ivin kav Zenith! Pahail za!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:42.62.0:01:44.62.Default..0.0.0..Ow. my eyes!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:44.62.0:01:46.99.Default..0.0.0..Am I still alive?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:48.41.0:01:53.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Zevaiah bazalfben kifu zivaikah kwav!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:49.20.0:01:53.54.Default..0.0.0..Hey. who's this guy?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:53.54.0:01:54.87.Default..0.0.0..Seriously?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:54.87.0:01:56.99.Default..0.0.0..I'm 100-plus kilos. and he lifted me like...
Dialogue: 0.0:01:56.37.0:02:01.12.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Bukay aiha naiboo!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:56.99.0:01:58.20.Default..0.0.0..Whoa! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:58.20.0:02:01.12.Default..0.0.0..Stop! That's gross!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:01.12.0:02:04.41.Default..0.0.0..What the hell? Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:02.54.0:02:06.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Zenith. tipen. eyuji. tawka paihail kwa.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:04.41.0:02:05.41.Default..0.0.0..Whoa.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:05.41.0:02:08.62.Default..0.0.0..What's she blushing like that for?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:10.16.0:02:11.99.Default..0.0.0..Her tits are huge.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:11.99.0:02:14.16.Default..0.0.0..Evun on. Nora iv aihen kap.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:14.16.0:02:15.83.Default..0.0.0..What language is that?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:15.83.0:02:19.99.Default..0.0.0..Wait. where am I? This isn't a hospital?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:19.99.0:02:23.79.Default..0.0.0..What the hell is he doing?\NI'm seriously injured.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:23.79.0:02:25.20.Default..0.0.0..Still. she's gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:25.20.0:02:26.70.Default..0.0.0..Is she European?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:26.70.0:02:30.37.Default..0.0.0..If you leave yourself that open.\NI might cop a feel.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:32.24.0:02:33.74.Default..0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:47.95.0:02:51.45.Default..0.0.0..It looks like I got reincarnated.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:51.45.0:02:55.45.Default..0.0.0..I can't believe something\Nthat crazy happened for real.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:55.45.0:03:00.41.Default..0.0.0..Paul and Zenith. In their mid-20s. I'd guess.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:57.12.0:02:58.29.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Moraiha kwa.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:58.29.0:02:59.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Zai.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:59.20.0:03:01.95.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Tawkah. za iksalaib.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:00.41.0:03:03.58.Default..0.0.0..I'm 34. so they're practically kids to me.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:01.95.0:03:05.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Zevaika vawksay Rudy!
Dialogue: 0.0:03:03.58.0:03:07.70.Default..0.0.0..I'm seriously jealous of them.\Nmaking babies at their age.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:07.70.0:03:11.29.Default..0.0.0..Still. getting to suck on\Na hottie's tits for free rules.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:11.29.0:03:15.79.Default..0.0.0..It didn't turn me on. though.\NMaybe 'cause she's my mom?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:17.20.0:03:18.70.Default..0.0.0..Rudy?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:18.70.0:03:20.74.Default..0.0.0..Where are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:20.74.0:03:21.95.Default..0.0.0..Rudeus?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:21.95.0:03:25.58.Default..0.0.0..I guess my name's "Rudeus."
Dialogue: 0.0:03:25.58.0:03:29.33.Default..0.0.0..After six months. I've got\Na pretty good grip on the language.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:29.33.0:03:33.95.Default..0.0.0..Maybe it's because I'm young.\Nbut I feel like I learn weirdly fast.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:43.24.0:03:45.24.Default..0.0.0..Lilia the maid.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:45.24.0:03:48.49.Default..0.0.0..She's wonderfully endowed.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:50.74.0:03:53.45.Default..0.0.0..Hey. Rudy!
Dialogue: 0.0:03:53.45.0:03:56.24.Default..0.0.0..You shouldn't wander around on your own.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:56.24.0:03:59.12.Default..0.0.0..This doesn't go on your head.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:59.12.0:04:01.91.Default..0.0.0..What's wrong. Lilia?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:01.91.0:04:05.70.Default..0.0.0..Lady Zenith. this is\Na little difficult to say. but...
Dialogue: 0.0:04:05.70.0:04:07.04.Default..0.0.0..Well...
Dialogue: 0.0:04:07.04.0:04:10.66.Default..0.0.0.....perhaps Master Rudeus is afflicted by some...
Dialogue: 0.0:04:10.66.0:04:13.20.Default..0.0.0..Oh. no. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:13.20.0:04:15.83.Default..0.0.0..What are you being evasive for?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:15.83.0:04:16.95.Default..0.0.0..He's a child.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:16.95.0:04:19.54.Default..0.0.0..He doesn't know any better.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:19.54.0:04:21.54.Default..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:29.20.0:04:31.20.Default..0.0.0..What a view.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:31.20.0:04:33.20.Default..0.0.0..I've seen photos like this.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:33.20.0:04:36.41.Default..0.0.0..Is this Europe. like I thought?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:36.41.0:04:38.12.Default..0.0.0..Still.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:36.95.0:04:38.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Do you think this is enough?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:38.12.0:04:41.12.Default..0.0.0..it's definitely {\i1}way{\i0} too rural.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:38.83.0:04:39.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:39.83.0:04:41.79.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}You handle that. then. Lilia.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:41.12.0:04:44.33.Default..0.0.0..No electricity or gas? What year is it?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:41.79.0:04:44.33.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Of course.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:44.33.0:04:48.29.Default..0.0.0..I might be reborn. but I still\Nwant to play with a computer.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:52.16.0:04:54.49.Default..0.0.0..Hey. what?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:55.54.0:04:57.41.Default..0.0.0..What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:58.66.0:05:00.33.Default..0.0.0..Oh crap.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:02.37.0:05:04.08.Default..0.0.0..Rudy?!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:04.66.0:05:05.16.Default..0.0.0..Rudy!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:05.16.0:05:06.54.Default..0.0.0..Young Master!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:08.99.0:05:10.99.Default..0.0.0..Is he all right?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:10.99.0:05:15.49.Default..0.0.0..You're not supposed to move\Npeople who've hit their heads. lady.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:15.49.0:05:18.66.Default..0.0.0..Even after that. he isn't crying.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:18.66.0:05:20.54.Default..0.0.0..There. there.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:20.54.0:05:22.49.Default..0.0.0..Just in case.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:22.49.0:05:26.95.Default..0.0.0..I'll do a spell to make the pain go away.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:34.41.0:05:37.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Divine power is rich and nourishing.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:36.91.0:05:38.66.Default..0.0.0..Hey. are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:38.66.0:05:41.70.Default..0.0.0..This is this country's\Nversion of kissing a boo boo?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:40.66.0:05:40.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}It offers the strength to rise again
Dialogue: 0.0:05:40.66.0:05:44.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}to those who have lost their strength.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:41.70.0:05:44.20.Default..0.0.0..Are both my parents delusional nerds?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:44.20.0:05:47.49.Default..0.0.0..Did the fighter marry the cleric?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:47.49.0:05:49.74.Default..0.0.0..Healing.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:02.41.0:06:05.29.Default..0.0.0..Well? It doesn't hurt anymore. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:05.29.0:06:08.37.Default..0.0.0..You wouldn't know it.\Nbut Mommy used to be an adventurer.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:08.37.0:06:09.29.Default..0.0.0..What is it?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:09.29.0:06:10.41.Default..0.0.0..I heard a loud--
Dialogue: 0.0:06:10.41.0:06:13.08.Default..0.0.0..Dear! Rudy fell on his head and...!
Dialogue: 0.0:06:13.08.0:06:16.29.Default..0.0.0..Calm down. He's a kid.\NOf course he'll fall down sometimes.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:16.29.0:06:19.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Besides. if he gets hurt.\Nyou can just heal him.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:17.37.0:06:19.62.Default..0.0.0..Don't tell me I'm in...
Dialogue: 0.0:06:19.62.0:06:23.16.Default..0.0.0..But what if he gets hurt\Nso badly that I can't heal him?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:23.16.0:06:25.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:23.74.0:06:26.58.Default..0.0.0..Actually. this pretty much confirms it.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:26.58.0:06:30.12.Default..0.0.0..This isn't Earth. It's another world.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:32.79.0:06:35.99.Default..0.0.0..A world of sword and sorcery.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:45.70.0:06:48.49.Default..0.0.0..I'm steady on my feet now.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:48.49.0:06:51.20.Default..0.0.0..Still. magic. huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:51.20.0:06:52.87.Default..0.0.0..Magic...
Dialogue: 0.0:06:54.12.0:06:57.12.Default..0.0.0..That's a word that'd get even a monkey excited.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:57.12.0:06:59.70.Default..0.0.0..I want to try it out myself ASAP.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:59.70.0:07:03.79.Default..0.0.0..That said. there's not much I can do right now.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:29.12.0:07:31.08.Default..0.0.0..Books?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:31.08.0:07:34.20.Default..0.0.0..There are only five books in the house.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:34.20.0:07:38.99.Default..0.0.0..Either books are expensive in this world.\Nor Paul and Zenith aren't big readers.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:38.99.0:07:43.16.Default..0.0.0..I used to have nearly a thousand.\Nso it's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:43.16.0:07:46.24.Default..0.0.0..All light novels. though.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:46.24.0:07:50.45.Default..0.0.0..I can't read it. I'll have\Nto learn to read first.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:51.66.0:07:53.99.Default..0.0.0..About another year passed.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:53.99.0:07:58.66.Default..0.0.0..Even with just five books. with the\Nhelp of Paul reading to me sometimes.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:58.66.0:08:01.37.Default..0.0.0..I can more-or-less read now.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:01.37.0:08:08.12.Default..0.0.0..Although I do wonder if he expects\Na baby to understand what's in these books.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:08.12.0:08:10.62.Default..0.0.0..Still. this book is fascinating.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:10.62.0:08:12.20.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}The Magic Manual{\i0} .
Dialogue: 0.0:08:12.20.0:08:14.79.Default..0.0.0..I've seen some of this stuff in my old life.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:14.79.0:08:19.87.Default..0.0.0..Like. there are two ways to activate magic:\Nincantations and magic circles.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:19.87.0:08:23.37.Default..0.0.0..but incantations dominate\Nthe mainstream right now. etc.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:23.37.0:08:25.62.Default..0.0.0..There's a lot of background.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:25.62.0:08:28.62.Default..0.0.0..But I'm more concerned that. according to this.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:28.62.0:08:31.99.Default..0.0.0..your magic power is\Nbasically set-in-stone at birth.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:31.99.0:08:33.20.Default..0.0.0..I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:33.20.0:08:36.41.Default..0.0.0..I doubt my genes are going to put in much work.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:36.41.0:08:39.74.Default..0.0.0..Well. I guess I'll give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:43.74.0:08:49.54.Default..0.0.0..Umm... "Let the great protection\Nof water be on the place thou seekest.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:49.54.0:08:53.41.Default..0.0.0..I call a refreshing.\Nburbling stream here and now.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:53.41.0:08:55.66.Default..0.0.0..Water Ball."
Dialogue: 0.0:09:14.91.0:09:17.29.Default..0.0.0..Shouldn't it go flying?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:20.12.0:09:22.08.Default..0.0.0..One more try.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:23.99.0:09:26.87.Default..0.0.0..It's like practicing combos in a fighter.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:26.87.0:09:30.74.Default..0.0.0..Concentrate. picture it over\Nand over in your head.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:30.74.0:09:33.20.Default..0.0.0..then actually do it.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:47.79.0:09:49.29.Default..0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:53.16.0:09:56.41.Default..0.0.0..I didn't do the incantation yet.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:56.41.0:09:58.04.Default..0.0.0..What gives?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:00.29.0:10:01.62.Default..0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:01.62.0:10:04.58.Default..0.0.0..This is all the MP I've got?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:06.58.0:10:08.49.Default..0.0.0..Honestly. Rudy.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:08.49.0:10:12.45.Default..0.0.0..If you're sleepy. you should go\Nto the bathroom and then to bed.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:12.45.0:10:13.74.Default..0.0.0..Damn it.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:13.74.0:10:16.66.Default..0.0.0..I'm too old to look like I wet myself!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:16.66.0:10:19.41.Default..0.0.0..Damn it. Damn it.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:23.16.0:10:25.12.Default..0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:32.20.0:10:34.54.Default..0.0.0..I experimented for a while and learned a lot.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:34.54.0:10:37.24.Default..0.0.0..This book's full of it!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:37.24.0:10:40.41.Default..0.0.0..Magic power grows the more you use it.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:40.41.0:10:42.66.Default..0.0.0..and magic works without incantations.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:42.66.0:10:46.12.Default..0.0.0..I guess I can't believe everything I read.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:46.12.0:10:51.37.Default..0.0.0..But if it's this easy.\Nwhat's even the point of incantations?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:54.08.0:10:59.20.Default..0.0.0..Maybe incantations are\Na system for automating magic.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:54.62.0:10:57.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Holy Millis who watches\Nover us in distant lands.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:57.66.0:11:01.24.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}we thank you for blessing us\Nwith life-giving nourishment.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:59.20.0:11:04.12.Default..0.0.0..They do it all for you without\Nthe need to focus on every single spell.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:01.24.0:11:04.12.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:04.12.0:11:07.45.Default..0.0.0..If so. there's a big advantage to them.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:07.45.0:11:09.41.Default..0.0.0..First. they're easy to teach.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:09.41.0:11:11.62.Default..0.0.0..An incantation is all you need to cast.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:11.62.0:11:13.33.Default..0.0.0..so as magic was taught.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:13.33.0:11:18.45.Default..0.0.0..maybe over time people started\Nto think incantations were necessary.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:18.45.0:11:20.16.Default..0.0.0..Second. convenience.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:20.16.0:11:23.04.Default..0.0.0..Attack magic is probably used in combat.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:21.79.0:11:29.74.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Thus. Perugius led his\N12 followers to the Devil Laplace.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:23.04.0:11:29.74.Default..0.0.0..and saying an incantation fast would\Nbe quicker than closing your eyes to focus.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:29.74.0:11:33.49.Default..0.0.0..I think it's your bedtime now. Rudy.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:33.49.0:11:35.58.Default..0.0.0..Dear. I can't take any more!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:35.58.0:11:38.74.Default..0.0.0..I'm just getting started.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:40.08.0:11:42.74.Default..0.0.0..My growing magic power is another mystery.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:42.74.0:11:45.87.Default..0.0.0..Could it be the result of my training?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:45.87.0:11:49.66.Default..0.0.0..There's supposed to be a cap on\Nmagic power. even if you work at it.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:49.66.0:11:52.54.Default..0.0.0..No. it's too soon to draw conclusions.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:52.54.0:11:56.49.Default..0.0.0..Yes. It could increase\Nas I grow up. for example.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:56.49.0:12:01.95.Default..0.0.0..Or maybe using magic at an early age\Ndramatically increases my maximum.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:01.95.0:12:03.33.Default..0.0.0..Oh.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:03.33.0:12:07.16.Default..0.0.0..I shouldn't discount the\Npossibility that I'm unique.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:07.16.0:12:09.45.Default..0.0.0..I've gotten into this!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:09.45.0:12:12.16.Default..0.0.0..Whoops. That's no good. Cool it.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:12.16.0:12:15.37.Default..0.0.0..If that hypothesis is right.\Nthere's only one thing to do:
Dialogue: 0.0:12:15.37.0:12:19.41.Default..0.0.0..Train as much as I can while I'm still growing.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:19.41.0:12:20.91.Default..0.0.0..Okay!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:22.33.0:12:25.74.Default..0.0.0..Still. how do I make these fly?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:40.70.0:12:42.20.Default..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:53.62.0:12:55.24.Default..0.0.0..Yes! All right!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:55.24.0:12:58.16.Default..0.0.0..I finally cracked how this incantation works.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:58.16.0:13:02.74.Default..0.0.0..This spell goes: create. set size.\Nset firing speed. activate.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:02.74.0:13:05.24.Default..0.0.0..That's the process it follows.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:05.24.0:13:07.91.Default..0.0.0..At least. I'm pretty sure that's it.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:07.91.0:13:12.08.Default..0.0.0..I didn't set the firing speed.\Nso it didn't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:17.12.0:13:22.04.Default..0.0.0..I've got more magic power now.\Nso it's time I tried intermediate magic.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:24.87.0:13:26.24.Default..0.0.0..Umm...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:26.24.0:13:31.66.Default..0.0.0.."Supple spirit of water and princess\Nof streams that flow through the earth.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:31.66.0:13:36.12.Default..0.0.0..sweep away all things\Nwith your hidden inner might.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:36.12.0:13:38.41.Default..0.0.0..Splash Flow."
Dialogue: 0.0:14:00.70.0:14:02.20.Default..0.0.0..What happened?!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:02.20.0:14:04.12.Default..0.0.0..H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:04.12.0:14:07.08.Default..0.0.0..What's going on?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:07.08.0:14:08.95.Default..0.0.0..Rudy?!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:08.95.0:14:09.99.Default..0.0.0..Rudy!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:09.99.0:14:10.95.Default..0.0.0..Are you hurt?!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:10.95.0:14:12.41.Default..0.0.0..N-No.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:12.41.0:14:14.37.Default..0.0.0..Was it a monster?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:14.37.0:14:17.66.Default..0.0.0..No. around here there aren't...
Dialogue: 0.0:14:17.66.0:14:19.24.Default..0.0.0..Oh?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:23.58.0:14:27.49.Default..0.0.0..Rudy. did you read this book out loud?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:27.49.0:14:28.62.Default..0.0.0..Huh? Scary.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:28.62.0:14:30.04.Default..0.0.0..What's that look?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:30.04.0:14:35.04.Default..0.0.0..Maybe kids who use magic are dangerous\Nand get sent off to an inquisition?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:35.04.0:14:37.62.Default..0.0.0..No! I don't want to get burned!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:40.54.0:14:42.95.Default..0.0.0..I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:42.95.0:14:44.33.Default..0.0.0..Did you hear that. dear?!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:44.33.0:14:46.70.Default..0.0.0..I knew our boy was a genius!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:46.70.0:14:49.08.Default..0.0.0..Hang on. This is an intermediate--
Dialogue: 0.0:14:49.08.0:14:51.37.Default..0.0.0..Let's hire a magic tutor right now!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:51.37.0:14:53.41.Default..0.0.0..But wait. we haven't even taught him to re--
Dialogue: 0.0:14:53.41.0:14:56.91.Default..0.0.0..I'm sure he'll grow up to be an amazing mage!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:58.16.0:15:01.87.Default..0.0.0..Wait a minute! We promised that\Nif it were a boy. he'd be a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:01.87.0:15:04.95.Default..0.0.0..But he can do intermediate magic at his age!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:04.95.0:15:06.45.Default..0.0.0..A promise is a promise!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:06.45.0:15:09.37.Default..0.0.0..You're one to talk!\NYou break yours all the time!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:09.37.0:15:12.29.Default..0.0.0..This has nothing to do with me!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:12.29.0:15:17.91.Default..0.0.0..Why not teach him magic in the morning\Nand swordsmanship in the afternoon?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:17.91.0:15:21.16.Default..0.0.0..It's not good to fight\Nin front of the baby. dear.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:21.16.0:15:23.37.Default..0.0.0..I guess not.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:23.37.0:15:26.79.Default..0.0.0..And so. we decided to hire me a magic tutor.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:26.79.0:15:29.54.Default..0.0.0..He spends all day at home swinging his sword.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:29.54.0:15:32.79.Default..0.0.0..but Paul's technically a knight\Nput in charge of this village.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:32.79.0:15:37.49.Default..0.0.0..I guess that's why he can\Nafford a tutor for a kid like me.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:37.49.0:15:41.20.Default..0.0.0..But this is the sticks on\Nthe edge of the country.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:41.20.0:15:43.45.Default..0.0.0..Will anyone actually apply out here?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:43.45.0:15:47.54.Default..0.0.0..Or so I worried. but they found one in no time.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:47.54.0:15:52.49.Default..0.0.0..My parents expected\Na retired adventurer to apply.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:48.33.0:15:50.08.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Good day.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:51.91.0:15:52.49.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Good day.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:52.49.0:15:57.49.Default..0.0.0..So. we figured on a middle-aged\Nor old man with a big. bushy beard.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:52.55.0:15:53.39.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Good day.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:57.49.0:16:01.54.Default..0.0.0..a veteran spellcaster who really screams "mage."
Dialogue: 0.0:16:01.54.0:16:03.45.Default..0.0.0..I'm Roxy Migurdia.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:03.45.0:16:05.41.Default..0.0.0..Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:07.83.0:16:09.20.Default..0.0.0..What the hell?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:09.20.0:16:12.74.Default..0.0.0..Forget a beard; she looks like\Nher bush hasn't grown in yet.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:12.74.0:16:14.04.Default..0.0.0..Maybe middle-school age?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:14.04.0:16:17.62.Default..0.0.0..Loli. scornful gaze. unsociable:\Nthree traits that equal perfection.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:17.62.0:16:19.08.Default..0.0.0..I want to marry her.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:19.08.0:16:22.29.Default..0.0.0..Oh. you're the. um... home tutor?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:22.29.0:16:23.83.Default..0.0.0..You're awfully. well...
Dialogue: 0.0:16:23.83.0:16:25.62.Default..0.0.0..She's tiny!
Dialogue: 0.0:16:25.62.0:16:28.29.Default..0.0.0..You're a fine one to talk.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:28.29.0:16:29.99.Default..0.0.0..Maybe she's sensitive about it?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:29.99.0:16:32.41.Default..0.0.0..I didn't mean her chest. though.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:32.41.0:16:35.62.Default..0.0.0..So. where is the student I'll be teaching?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:35.62.0:16:38.16.Default..0.0.0..Oh. he's right here!
Dialogue: 0.0:16:40.45.0:16:42.45.Default..0.0.0..You do see them sometimes.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:42.45.0:16:46.91.Default..0.0.0..Idiot parents who think their kid has\Ntalent just because he's an early bloomer.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:46.91.0:16:49.45.Default..0.0.0..We can hear you. Roxy!
Dialogue: 0.0:16:47.66.0:16:49.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Looks like this one's a dud.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:49.45.0:16:51.08.Default..0.0.0..Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:51.08.0:16:52.08.Default..0.0.0..Nothing!
Dialogue: 0.0:16:52.08.0:16:56.83.Default..0.0.0..Only. I doubt that child could\Ncomprehend the theory of magic.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:56.83.0:17:01.49.Default..0.0.0..Don't worry! Our little Rudy is amazing!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:02.74.0:17:06.70.Default..0.0.0..I understand. I'll do what I can.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:06.70.0:17:08.62.Default..0.0.0..Huh? We're doing it outside?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:08.62.0:17:11.37.Default..0.0.0..Naturally.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:16.91.0:17:20.83.Default..0.0.0..In broad terms. there are\Nonly three types of magic.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:20.83.0:17:24.37.Default..0.0.0..Attack magic. healing magic.\Nand summoning magic.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:24.37.0:17:27.54.Default..0.0.0..Each is divided into seven ranks:
Dialogue: 0.0:17:27.54.0:17:33.20.Default..0.0.0..beginner. intermediate. advanced.\Nsacred. royal. imperial. and divine.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:33.20.0:17:36.70.Default..0.0.0..And to use magic. you need magical power.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:36.70.0:17:40.12.Default..0.0.0..Either the magical power within you. or...
Dialogue: 0.0:17:40.12.0:17:41.45.Default..0.0.0..Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:41.45.0:17:43.58.Default..0.0.0..Oh. no.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:44.54.0:17:45.79.Default..0.0.0..All right. then.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:45.79.0:17:49.87.Default..0.0.0..Anyway. I'll start by demonstrating\Nan incantation. so repeat after me.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:49.87.0:17:53.16.Default..0.0.0..Do you need the incantation?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:53.16.0:17:54.95.Default..0.0.0..Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:54.95.0:17:57.16.Default..0.0.0..I thought so.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:59.41.0:18:03.37.Default..0.0.0..Let the great protection of water\Nbe on the place thou seekest.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:03.37.0:18:06.29.Default..0.0.0..I call a refreshing.\Nburbling stream here and now.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:06.29.0:18:08.33.Default..0.0.0..Water Ball!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:13.49.0:18:14.87.Default..0.0.0..What do you think?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:14.87.0:18:20.62.Default..0.0.0..Miss. my mom worked hard to raise\Nthat tree. so I think she'll get mad.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:20.62.0:18:21.70.Default..0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:21.70.0:18:25.24.Default..0.0.0..Th-That won't do. will it?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:25.24.0:18:28.16.Default..0.0.0..Divine power is rich and nourishing.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:28.16.0:18:32.74.Default..0.0.0..It offers the strength to rise again\Nto those who have lost their strength.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:32.74.0:18:34.33.Default..0.0.0..Healing!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:35.83.0:18:37.83.Default..0.0.0..Oh. wow.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:37.83.0:18:40.24.Default..0.0.0..You can use healing magic. too!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:40.24.0:18:42.04.Default..0.0.0..Yes. up to intermediate level.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:42.04.0:18:44.16.Default..0.0.0..Wow! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:44.16.0:18:49.12.Default..0.0.0..No. anyone can do as much\Nif they train properly.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:49.12.0:18:51.83.Default..0.0.0..She seems like a pushover.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:51.83.0:18:53.49.Default..0.0.0..Now. you try it.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:53.49.0:18:54.87.Default..0.0.0..Okay!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:56.62.0:19:00.45.Default..0.0.0..The Magic Manual didn't mention\Nincantation-less spells either.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:00.45.0:19:05.04.Default..0.0.0..I'd been using them without thinking.\Nbut maybe that's taboo.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:05.04.0:19:07.62.Default..0.0.0..Roxy said you need incantations. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:07.62.0:19:10.24.Default..0.0.0..so I should say them for now.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:10.24.0:19:12.45.Default..0.0.0..They could be important.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:12.45.0:19:16.91.Default..0.0.0..Let the great protection of water\Nbe on the place thou seekest...
Dialogue: 0.0:19:21.62.0:19:22.91.Default..0.0.0..What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:22.91.0:19:24.74.Default..0.0.0..Oh. n-nothing!
Dialogue: 0.0:19:24.74.0:19:26.20.Default..0.0.0..How did I do?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:27.33.0:19:29.87.Default..0.0.0..You cut the incantation short.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:29.87.0:19:30.83.Default..0.0.0..I did.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:30.83.0:19:33.45.Default..0.0.0..Do you always abridge it like that?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:33.45.0:19:36.49.Default..0.0.0..I usually... just skip it.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:36.49.0:19:38.87.Default..0.0.0..Completely?!
Dialogue: 0.0:19:38.87.0:19:42.79.Default..0.0.0..So. you usually omit the incantation.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:42.79.0:19:44.83.Default..0.0.0..I see.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:44.83.0:19:48.04.Default..0.0.0..It looks like you'll be worth training.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:53.24.0:19:54.62.Default..0.0.0..Oh.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:58.24.0:20:01.62.Default..0.0.0..Roxy! Don't use my trees as test subjects!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:01.62.0:20:02.16.Default..0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:02.16.0:20:03.45.Default..0.0.0..Oh. honestly!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:05.62.0:20:09.54.Default..0.0.0..I screwed up right away.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:09.54.0:20:11.74.Default..0.0.0..I guess I'll be fired tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:11.74.0:20:15.70.Default..0.0.0..I'm sorry. miss. It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:15.70.0:20:20.04.Default..0.0.0..Damn it. I hadn't had a\Nconversation in almost 20 years.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:20.04.0:20:23.49.Default..0.0.0..I don't know what to say at times like this.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:23.49.0:20:26.95.Default..0.0.0..No. think. You've done this lots of times.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:26.95.0:20:30.29.Default..0.0.0..What would a dating sim\Nprotagonist do in this situation?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:32.33.0:20:38.37.Default..0.0.0..You didn't screw up. miss.\Nyou gained experience.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:41.41.0:20:43.87.Default..0.0.0..I-I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:43.87.0:20:46.16.Default..0.0.0..Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:53.58.0:20:54.87.Default..0.0.0..Ow!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:56.66.0:20:58.04.Default..0.0.0..More importantly. Roxy.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:58.04.0:20:59.04.Default..0.0.0..Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:59.04.0:21:00.83.Default..0.0.0..Let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:00.83.0:21:04.29.Default..0.0.0..Let's start by introducing ourselves. okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:06.66.0:21:08.45.Default..0.0.0..Hey!
Dialogue: 0.0:21:08.45.0:21:10.66.Default..0.0.0..Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0.0:21:13.04.0:21:16.62.Default..0.0.0..I'm grateful. but I have\Nnothing to offer you in return.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:16.62.0:21:17.99.Default..0.0.0..Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:17.99.0:21:20.16.Default..0.0.0..Now. come on in.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:22.24.0:21:24.08.Default..0.0.0..You. too. Rudy.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:24.08.0:21:25.87.Default..0.0.0..Okay!
Dialogue: 0.0:21:32.83.0:21:37.99.Default..0.0.0..Okay. let's get Roxy's welcome party started!
Dialogue: 0.0:21:37.99.0:21:40.33.Default..0.0.0..It's like a dream.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:40.33.0:21:43.04.Default..0.0.0..A dream I'm having as I die from that crash.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:43.04.0:21:43.95.Default..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:43.95.0:21:46.54.Default..0.0.0..Even if it is. I don't care.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:46.54.0:21:50.41.Default..0.0.0..In this world. I bet even I can make it.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:50.41.0:21:53.12.Default..0.0.0..If I live and try as hard as everyone else.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:53.12.0:21:57.62.Default..0.0.0..get back up when I fall.\Nand keep facing forward.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:57.62.0:21:59.49.Default..0.0.0..then maybe I can do it.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:59.49.0:22:01.45.Default..0.0.0..Maybe even I...
Dialogue: 0.0:22:01.45.0:22:04.49.Default..0.0.0..Maybe even a jobless. reclusive bum like me
Dialogue: 0.0:22:04.49.0:22:07.24.Default..0.0.0..can get a do-over at life...
Dialogue: 0.0:22:09.01.0:22:12.01.Default..0.0.0..{\fs60\bord0\pos(642.260)}Episode 1
Dialogue: 0.0:22:09.01.0:22:12.01.Default..0.0.0..{\blur1\shad3\fs60\bord0\pos(646.504)\4c&H000000&\3c&H4C4D50&}Jobless Reincarnation
Dialogue: 0.0:22:09.33.0:22:12.04.Default..0.0.0.....and can get serious about living.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:35.95.0:23:42.04.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}"Mushoku Tensei: Jobless Reincarnation"
Dialogue: 0.0:23:42.04.0:23:47.03.Default..0.0.0..{\fs30\bord0.1\pos(640.250)\fnOpen Sans Light\b0\c&H020A43&\3c&H020A43&}Next time
Dialogue: 0.0:23:42.44.0:23:47.03.Default..0.0.0..{\fad(500.0)\fs60\bord0.2\fnOpen Sans\b0\c&H020A43&\3c&H020A43&\pos(638.450)}Teacher
